data.description: Spectacular custom built home with high-end finishes situated on a 1.16 acre fenced and landscaped lot.  This 4 bedroom, 4 bathroom nearly 3000 sq.ft. house features granite countertops, custom shaker cabinets, alder doors and trim, an eight burner gas range, side-by-side ovens and a walk-in pantry.  Above the three car garage is a huge bonus room with its own half bath.  The master bathroom includes a large soaking tub and spacious walk-in closet.  Gorgeous mountain views, privacy and less than ten minutes to the heart of Kalispell, this property has it all.  Please call Melissa Santa at 406-212-3676, or your real estate professional.
